---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Committees - Fells Prospect Community Association"
  description="Learn about the committees that serve the Fells Prospect community and how to get involved."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="relative py-20 md:py-28" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C1503D 0%, #A84636 100%);">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #FAF8F4;">
        Our Committees
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl max-w-3xl mx-auto" style="color: #EFE9DC;">
        Get involved with FPCA committees serving our community
      </p>
    </div>
    <!-- Decorative bottom -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-full">
        <path d="M0 0L60 5C120 10 240 20 360 23.3C480 27 600 23 720 21.7C840 20 960 20 1080 23.3C1200 27 1320 33 1380 36.7L1440 40V60H0V0Z" fill="#FAF8F4"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Beautification Committee -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20" style="background-color: #FAF8F4;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Committee Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-block p-4 rounded-full mb-6" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1B365D, #4A7C9D);">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12" style="color: #D4A574;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #3D3D3D;">
          Beautification
        </h2>
        <div class="w-32 h-1 mx-auto" style="background-color: #D4A574;"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content Grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-start mb-12">
        <!-- Text Content -->
        <div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 md:p-10" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #F5F1E8, #EFE9DC);">
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: #3D3D3D;">
              As a cherished landmark of the mid-Atlantic region and an important relic of American history, Fells Prospect presents attractive architecture in an enjoyable climate, year round. Our association sponsors events to improve our physical neighborhood in several ways. We would love to have your participation in our efforts promote enjoyable life in our shared space.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #C1503D;">
              Here are some ways you can get involved:
            </h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Image -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl" style="border: 4px solid #1B365D;">
          <img
            src="/images/Clean Up Crew from Cristo Rey.jpg"
            alt="Students from Cristo Rey joined us for a community cleanup event"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
          <div class="p-4" style="background-color: #1B365D; color: #FAF8F4;">
            <p class="text-sm">
              Students from the local high school, Cristo Rey, joined us for a community cleanup event
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Ways to Get Involved -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- Love Your Block -->
        <div class="rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 transition-transform hover:scale-105" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C1503D, #A84636); color: #FAF8F4;">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4" style="background-color: #D4A574;">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" style="color: #3D3D3D;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">"Love Your Block" 2024</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Grant application process opens in March.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Dumpster Days -->
        <div class="rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 transition-transform hover:scale-105" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1B365D, #4A7C9D); color: #FAF8F4;">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4" style="background-color: #D4A574;">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" style="color: #3D3D3D;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">2024 Dumpster Days</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Have been announced.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Cafe Lighting -->
        <div class="rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 transition-transform hover:scale-105" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D4A574, #B8914E); color: #3D3D3D;">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4" style="background-color: #FAF8F4;">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" style="color: #D4A574;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">Cafe Lighting</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Enhancing our neighborhood ambiance with beautiful outdoor lighting.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Community Cleanup -->
        <div class="rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 transition-transform hover:scale-105" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C1503D, #A84636); color: #FAF8F4;">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4" style="background-color: #D4A574;">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" style="color: #3D3D3D;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">Community Cleanup Events</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Join neighbors in keeping Fells Prospect clean and beautiful.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Safety Committee -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #EFE9DC, #F5F1E8);">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Committee Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-block p-4 rounded-full mb-6" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C1503D, #A84636);">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12" style="color: #D4A574;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #3D3D3D;">
          Safety
        </h2>
        <div class="w-32 h-1 mx-auto" style="background-color: #D4A574;"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content Grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-start mb-12">
        <!-- Text Content -->
        <div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 md:p-10" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #F5F1E8, #EFE9DC);">
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: #3D3D3D;">
              The Safety Committee works to keep our neighborhood secure and welcoming for all residents. We collaborate with local law enforcement, organize community watch programs, and address safety concerns to ensure Fells Prospect remains a safe place to live, work, and visit.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #C1503D;">
              Safety Initiatives:
            </h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Image -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl" style="border: 4px solid #C1503D;">
          <img
            src="/images/national-night-out.avif"
            alt="National Night Out community safety event"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
          <div class="p-4" style="background-color: #C1503D; color: #FAF8F4;">
            <p class="text-sm">
              Residents gather for National Night Out to build community connections and promote neighborhood safety
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Safety Initiatives -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- Neighborhood Watch -->
        <div class="rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 transition-transform hover:scale-105" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C1503D, #A84636); color: #FAF8F4;">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4" style="background-color: #D4A574;">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" style="color: #3D3D3D;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">Neighborhood Watch</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Active community monitoring to deter crime and maintain a visible presence in our streets.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Safety Walks -->
        <div class="rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 transition-transform hover:scale-105" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1B365D, #4A7C9D); color: #FAF8F4;">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4" style="background-color: #D4A574;">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" style="color: #3D3D3D;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">Community Safety Walks</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Regular neighborhood walks to build connections and increase visibility.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Crime Reporting -->
        <div class="rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 transition-transform hover:scale-105" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D4A574, #B8914E); color: #3D3D3D;">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4" style="background-color: #FAF8F4;">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" style="color: #D4A574;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">Crime Reporting & Alerts</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Stay informed with timely alerts and learn how to report suspicious activity effectively.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Street Lighting -->
        <div class="rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 transition-transform hover:scale-105" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C1503D, #A84636); color: #FAF8F4;">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4" style="background-color: #D4A574;">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" style="color: #3D3D3D;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">Street Lighting Improvements</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Advocating for better street lighting to enhance safety and visibility after dark.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Community Engagement Committee -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20" style="background-color: #FAF8F4;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Committee Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-block p-4 rounded-full mb-6" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D4A574, #B8914E);">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12" style="color: #3D3D3D;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #3D3D3D;">
          Community Engagement
        </h2>
        <div class="w-32 h-1 mx-auto" style="background-color: #D4A574;"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content Grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-start mb-12">
        <!-- Text Content -->
        <div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 md:p-10" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #F5F1E8, #EFE9DC);">
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: #3D3D3D;">
              We are neighbors helping neighbors enjoy our neighborhood! We believe this includes everyone. We believe the best investment in our community is through developing relationships and connecting our community with resources to stay informed, access resources and have fun!
            </p>

            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: #3D3D3D;">
              Come be a part of our mission to connect neighbors. We are seeking volunteers for the following endeavors:
            </p>

            <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg" style="color: #3D3D3D;">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-3" style="color: #D4A574;">•</span>
                <span>Delivery of our printed newsletter each month.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-3" style="color: #D4A574;">•</span>
                <span>Assistance maintaining our website and social media presence.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-3" style="color: #D4A574;">•</span>
                <span>Fundraising with local businesses.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-3" style="color: #D4A574;">•</span>
                <span>Bringing our meetings into the online space.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Image -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl" style="border: 4px solid #D4A574;">
          <img
            src="/images/people.avif"
            alt="Community members connecting and building relationships"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
          <div class="p-4" style="background-color: #D4A574; color: #3D3D3D;">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold">
              Building strong connections between neighbors in Fells Prospect
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1B365D 0%, #4A7C9D 100%); color: #FAF8F4;">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">Want to Get Involved?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8" style="color: #EFE9DC;">
        Join one of our committees and help make Fells Prospect an even better place to call home!
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 font-semibold rounded-lg transition-all shadow-lg text-lg" style="background-color: #FAF8F4; color: #1B365D;" onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#EFE9DC'" onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#FAF8F4'">
        Contact Us to Join
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
